l sought after at high level.  If your bored with your necro, and want do a little soloing from time to time this is a good class.  Otherwise stick to the base Warrior/cleric/rogue/chanter/shamy bunch. <p>Macalister WolfGuard -42nd Warrior /Morteux Thantos 52nd Heritic /Ardin Macalister 35th Bard/Clanncy Macalroy 32nd Beastlord(Saryrn) Questing to be the #1 Barbarian BL on the server.</p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#6FB8DD>- </font><a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/bthesaryrntavern>The Saryrn Tavern</a><font color=#6FB8DD> - </font><a href=http://pub40.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernfrm16>Expansion Discussions</a><font color=#6FB8DD> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.3m<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  

